<view class="page">
  <view class="nav">
    <view class="back" bindtap="onBack">‹</view>
    <text>舌象测评</text>
  </view>

  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-copy">
      <text class="hero-kicker">AI 舌象分析</text>
      <text class="hero-title">拍摄舌象，洞察体质</text>
      <text class="hero-desc">请将舌面放入取景框内，保持光线充足，尽量露出完整舌根。</text>
    </view>
    <image class="hero-art" src="../../assets/images/feature-tongue-lite.jpg" mode="aspectFit" />
  </view>

  <view class="capture-card">
    <view class="scan-frame">
      <view class="corner lt"></view>
      <view class="corner rt"></view>
      <view class="corner lb"></view>
      <view class="corner rb"></view>
      <view class="tongue-outline">
        <view class="tongue-line"></view>
      </view>
      <text class="scan-tip">请对准舌面区域</text>
    </view>
    <view class="safe-note">
      <text>温馨提示：该内容仅供参考，不构成医疗诊断/治疗建议，如有不适请及时前往正规医疗机构就诊。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-title">
      <view></view>
      <text>拍摄注意事项</text>
    </view>
    <view class="tips">
      <view class="tip-row" wx:for="{{tips}}" wx:key="title">
        <text class="tip-index">{{index + 1}}</text>
        <view>
          <text class="tip-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="tip-desc">{{item.desc}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="action-card">
    <view class="camera-btn" bindtap="onTakePhoto">
      <text class="camera-icon">⌾</text>
      <text>开始拍摄</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
